msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Whose’s calling you in? Language, People and Technology"
msgstr "Kukubali urafiki muhimu. Lugha, Watu na Teknolojia"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Thoughts on the State of Internet Languages Report from the Mozilla Common Voice Team."
msgstr "Mawazo juu ya Ripoti ya Hali ya Lugha za Intaneti kutoka kwa Timu ya Sauti ya Kawaida ya Mozilla."

msgctxt "body.bc66396d-04ec-4498-b401-21eb7dbf763f"
msgid ""
"Preface: This OP-Ed includes a glossary of terms to explain phrases used to support you as a reader to understand the content. If you are new to the interdisciplinary analysis of technology, "
"language and power, I would like to encourage you to check out the glossary."
msgstr ""
"Dibaji: Makala haya ya Maoni yanajumuisha faharasa ya maneno ili kuelezea misemo inayotumiwa ili isaidie msomaji kuelewa yaliyomo. Ikiwa wewe ni mgeni wa uchambuzi wa nyanja mbalimbali za "
"teknolojia, lugha na nguvu, ningependa kukuhimiza uangalie faharasa ya istilahi."

msgctxt "body.bc66396d-04ec-4498-b401-21eb7dbf763f"
msgid "If we don’t maintain critical friendships, we impose liberation. Whose words, whose languages are we prioritising when working towards Trustworthy AI?"
msgstr "Tusipodumisha urafiki muhimu, tunalazimisha watu wawe huru. Je, tunapea kipaumbele maneno ya nani, lugha gani tunaposhughulikia AI Inayoaminika?"

msgctxt "body.bc66396d-04ec-4498-b401-21eb7dbf763f"
msgid ""
"At the end of February, <a id=\"a1\"><i>Whose Knowledge?</i></a>, <a id=\"a2\">The Centre for Internet &amp; Society (India)</a> and <a id=\"a3\">Oxford Internet Institute</a> launched the <a "
"id=\"a4\">State of the Internet Languages</a> (STIL) report. As a reviewer of the report, I was humbled and refreshed to see the stories of language communities platformed honourably, and in their "
"mother tongues."
msgstr ""
"Mwishoni mwa Februari, Maarifa ya <a id=\"a1\"><i>nani?</i></a>, Kituo <a id=\"a2\">cha Intaneti na Jamii (India)</a> na <a id=\"a3\">Taasisi ya Intaneti ya Oxford</a> ilizindua <a id=\"a4\">Ripoti "
"ya Hali ya Lugha za Mtandao</a> (STIL). Kama mhakiki wa ripoti hiyo, nilivutiwa na nilifurahi sana kuona hadithi za jamii za lugha zikiwasilishwa kwa heshima, na katika lugha zao za asili."

msgctxt "body.bc66396d-04ec-4498-b401-21eb7dbf763f"
msgid ""
"The STIL report challenges how power operates across the process of including and excluding spoken and signed languages on the internet. STIL contributors analyse the exclusionary aspects of "
"language inequity online: from the <a id=\"a1\">Latin-centrism of UNICODE</a> to <a id=\"a2\">marginalisations of queerness and disability</a> in search engines to the lack of agency and "
"sociolinguistic <a id=\"a3\">context</a> in the development of tools, data and software."
msgstr ""
"Ripoti ya STIL inapinga jinsi nguvu inavyochangia katika mchakato wote wa kujumuisha na kutojumuisha lugha zinazozungumzwa na lugha za ishara kwenye mtandao. Wachangiaji wa STIL wanachambua "
"vipengele vya kutojumuisha lugha kwa usawa mtandaoni: kutoka <a id=\"a1\">Msimamo wa katiwa MSIMBOSARE wa Kilatini</a> hadi <a id=\"a2\">kutenga watu wasio wa kawaida na ulemavu</a> katika injini za"
" utaftaji hadi ukosefu wa maudhui ya mashirika na isimu jamii <a id=\"a3\">katika</a> utengenezaji wa zana, data na programu."

msgctxt "body.bc66396d-04ec-4498-b401-21eb7dbf763f"
msgid "Hear from Ishan, sharing their experience at the State of the Internet Languages Report Launch (Timestamp: 31:44)"
msgstr "Sikia kutoka kwa Ishan, wakishiriki mambo waliyopitia katika Uzinduzi wa Ripoti ya Hali ya Lugha za Mtandao (Muda: 31: 44)"

